#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/za4fENHuX9SDv0qpFjP6EquJeHS.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="Une agente des forces de l'ordre est chargée d'assurer la sécurité de Winston, un criminel qui a accepté de témoigner dans une affaire de corruption. Ce dernier vient d'être arrêté et doit être transporté jusqu'à Anchorage, en Alaska. Tous deux prennent place à bord d'un petit avion de brousse. Alors qu'ils traversent une zone de turbulences, le permis de pilotage du pilote glisse sur le sol. La photo d'identité qui s'y trouve ne correspond pas à l'homme qui tient les commandes de l'appareil." year="2025-01-22" director="Mel Gibson" actors="Mark Wahlberg, Michelle Dockery, Topher Grace, Leah Remini, Maaz Ali, Paul Ben-Victor, Eilise Patton, Senor Pablo, Savanah Joeckel, Mark 'Cowboy' Schotz",FR - Vol à haut risque (2025)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1790125.mkv&play_token=eS6FirmLZN&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/260GDjmYf2A9W09RRo5FwUueQ3Y.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="Eleven-year-old Mildred’s life is turned upside down when her mother lands in hospital and estranged, American magician father, Strawn Wise, comes to look after her.  Hoping to entertain the bookish tween, Strawn takes Mildred camping in the notoriously rugged New Zealand wilderness, and the pair embark on the ultimate test of family bonding – a quest to find the mythological beast known as the Canterbury Panther." year="2024-07-04" director="Ant Timpson" actors="Nell Fisher, Elijah Wood, Michael Smiley, Vanessa Stacey, Morgana O'Reilly",Bookworm (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1790123.mkv&play_token=DI0n4KsPRX&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/qtuzj4BFRfnzfeUPLITgj7Mk1U.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="Apprenant l'implication de son ennemi juré Donnie Wilson dans un audacieux vol de diamants en Belgique, Nick O'Brien, shérif à Los Angeles, s'envole pour l'Europe. Il repère rapidement Donnie à Nice et, jouant le jeu du flic en instance de divorce désabusé et pourri, le convainc de l'intégrer dans sa bande. Celle-ci planifie un gros cambriolage dans le centre mondial du diamant de la cité méditerranéenne." year="2025-01-08" director="Christian Gudegast" actors="Gerard Butler, O'Shea Jackson Jr., Evin Ahmad, Salvatore Esposito, Orli Shuka, Stéphane Coulon, Cristian Solimeno, Nazmiye Oral, Mark Grosy, Joshua Gabriel Liège",FR - Criminal Squad : Pantera (2025)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1781057.mkv&play_token=TQ5cvZ4TsT&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/20lz5Ld3ulxVPQTX5p9DvD1hgk1.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="Pour empêcher un trafiquant de livrer une arme de destruction massive, le tireur d'élite Brandon Beckett et l'agent Zero dirigent un groupe de soldats au Costa Verde. Avec un jeune tireur d'élite sous son aile, Beckett doit relever un défi: donner des ordres au lieu d'en recevoir. Avec le temps et les munitions qui manquent, survivre sera un défi de taille." year="2025-01-21" director="Danishka Esterhazy" actors="Chad Michael Collins, Ryan Robbins, Sharon Taylor, Manuel Rodriguez-Saenz, Scott George, Vusi Kunene, Sizo Mahlangu, Noxolo Dlamini, Arnold Vosloo, Rob van Vuuren",FR - Sniper: The Last Stand (2025)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1771227.mkv&play_token=Ybw2oyHOK3&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/chh2xSTVtMCFyFePm1zRbBmtqaX.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="A raw urban drama about two friends raised on the dangerous streets of Kingston, Jamaica. Biggs and Wayne take on the 'Shotta' way of life to survive. As young boys, they begin a life of crime, eventually moving to the US where they begin a ruthless climb from the bottom. They remain bound to each other by their shottas loyalty as they aggressively take control of the Jamaican underworld." year="2002-02-27" director="Adam Doench, Lyndale V. Pettus, Cess Silvera" actors="Ky-Mani Marley, Spragga Benz, Paul Campbell, Louie Rankin, Wyclef Jean",Shottas (2002)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1769080.mkv&play_token=tOF6zSBpKl&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/v313aUGmMNj6yNveaiQXysBmjVS.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="Joe et Lara Travers, deux assassins amoureux, sont témoins d'un accident d'avion et récupèrent une clé USB dans l'appareil accidenté. Ils découvrent que le contenu va mettre toutes les agences de renseignement du monde à leurs trousses, y compris Chester, un agent de la CIA au sang froid, qui a été envoyé pour les assassiner." year="2025-01-16" director="Michael Polish" actors="Scott Eastwood, Sylvester Stallone, Willa Fitzgerald, Mike Colter, D.W. Moffett, Isis Valverde, Anton Narinskiy, Patrick Millin, Joel Cohen, La Monde Byrd",FR - Alarum (2025)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1769060.mkv&play_token=5caUAtXzKr&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/aSUp3dZpiEeWw0LQEN9zcdbI27r.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="Un homme se réveille dans une ville inconnue. Il ignore qui il est et doit percer des mystères pour découvrir son identité. Lors des recherches concernant son passé, il se retrouve confronté à un puissant ennemi. Leur affrontement final scellera son sort et lui permettra de découvrir son identité." year="2025-01-13" director="James Bamford" actors="Tim Fellingham, Philip Winchester, Nathan Cooper, Adam Woodward, Nico Seedsman, Jeff Alexander, Joseph Al Ahmad",FR - Man with No Past (2025)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1767237.mkv&play_token=7EHUdadSjG&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/1GvBhRxY6MELDfxFrete6BNhBB5.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="Kraven Kravinoff's complex relationship with his ruthless gangster father, Nikolai, starts him down a path of vengeance with brutal consequences, motivating him to become not only the greatest hunter in the world, but also one of its most feared." year="2024-12-11" director="Carley Armstrong, Paula Casarin, Andrea Trigo, Martina Vazzoler, J.C. Chandor" actors="Aaron Taylor-Johnson, Ariana DeBose, Fred Hechinger, Alessandro Nivola, Christopher Abbott",Kraven the Hunter (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1765434.mkv&play_token=92cl1eOvDR&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/u0Ct3708zXaoJCkF65bLfenQmhM.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="À la fin des années 80, Oh Dae-Soo, père de famille sans histoire, est enlevé un jour devant chez lui. Séquestré pendant plusieurs années dans une cellule privée, son seul lien avec l'extérieur est une télévision. Par le biais de cette télévision, il apprend le meurtre de sa femme, meurtre dont il est le principal suspect. Au désespoir d'être séquestré sans raison apparente succède alors chez le héros une rage intérieure vengeresse qui lui permet de survivre. Il est relâché 15 ans plus tard, toujours sans explication. Oh Dae-Soo est alors contacté par celui qui semble être le responsable de ses malheurs, qui lui propose de découvrir qui l'a enlevé et pourquoi. Le cauchemar continue pour le héros." year="2003-11-21" director="Park Chan-wook" actors="Choi Min-sik, Yoo Ji-tae, Kang Hye-jung, Kim Byeong-ok, Ji Dae-han, Oh Dal-su, Lee Seung-shin, Yoon Jin-seo, Oh Tae-kyung, Yoo Yeon-seok",FR - Old Boy (2003)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1754431.mkv&play_token=h6TAq9Nalx&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/tjK063yCgaBAluVU72rZ6PKPH2l.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="Throughout his life Edward Bloom has always been a man of big appetites, enormous passions and tall tales. In his later years, he remains a huge mystery to his son, William. Now, to get to know the real man, Will begins piecing together a true picture of his father from flashbacks of his amazing adventures." year="2003-12-25" director="Tim Burton, Janna Stern, Katterli Frauenfelder, Vanessa Mujica, Carlos De La Torre" actors="Ewan McGregor, Albert Finney, Billy Crudup, Jessica Lange, Helena Bonham Carter",Big Fish (2003)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1754418.mkv&play_token=ksv3v814KV&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/50kALxDX4mmzIRljbNbPY0u4cie.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="Some of Sin City's most hard-boiled citizens cross paths with a few of its more reviled inhabitants." year="2014-08-20" director="Robert Rodriguez, Frank Miller, Monika Petrillo" actors="Jessica Alba, Bruce Willis, Mickey Rourke, Josh Brolin, Joseph Gordon-Levitt",Sin City: A Dame to Kill For (2014)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1749055.mkv&play_token=kR0Dy7ohvD&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/1avD1JeaRiJX5M4ahPdZPypGoGN.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="In a world in which Great Britain has become a fascist state, a masked vigilante known only as “V” conducts guerrilla warfare against the oppressive British government. When V rescues a young woman from the secret police, he finds in her an ally with whom he can continue his fight to free the people of Britain." year="2006-02-23" director="James McTeigue, Jean Bourne, Julie Brown, Michael Stevenson, Terry Needham" actors="Natalie Portman, Hugo Weaving, Stephen Rea, Stephen Fry, John Hurt",V for Vendetta (2006)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1735605.mkv&play_token=CNSwgaWUeU&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/fxRIpx9Op9h71q3tvuabx4GryyP.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="Speed Racer is a young and brilliant racing driver. When corruption in the racing leagues costs his brother his life, Speed must team up with the police and the mysterious Racer X to bring an end to the corruption and criminal activities." year="2008-05-07" director="Lana Wachowski, Lilly Wachowski, Terry Needham, Emma Horton" actors="Emile Hirsch, Christina Ricci, John Goodman, Susan Sarandon, Matthew Fox",Speed Racer (2008)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1735599.mkv&play_token=dTH5MfujFV&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/i66G50wATMmPrvpP95f0XP6ZdVS.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="Welcome to Sin City. This town beckons to the tough, the corrupt, the brokenhearted. Some call it dark… Hard-boiled. Then there are those who call it home — Crooked cops, sexy dames, desperate vigilantes. Some are seeking revenge, others lust after redemption, and then there are those hoping for a little of both. A universe of unlikely and reluctant heroes still trying to do the right thing in a city that refuses to care." year="2005-04-01" director="Robert Rodriguez, Frank Miller, Monika Petrillo, Quentin Tarantino, Brian Bettwy" actors="Bruce Willis, Jessica Alba, Clive Owen, Mickey Rourke, Rutger Hauer",Sin City (2005)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1735598.mkv&play_token=4hbmwnOOBB&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/onQTiwGNXr46bq2R39JIIAy26fu.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="Quelques semaines après les attentats du 11 septembre 2001, un détachement d'élite des Forces Spéciales a été envoyé en Afghanistan, en plein conflit, pour une périlleuse mission top-secrète : apporter leur aide aux Afghans dans leur lutte contre les talibans et leurs alliés d'Al Quaïda." year="2018-01-18" director="Nicolai Fuglsig" actors="Chris Hemsworth, Michael Shannon, Michael Peña, Navid Negahban, Trevante Rhodes, Geoff Stults, Thad Luckinbill, Austin Stowell, Ben O'Toole, Jack Kesy",FR - Horse Soldiers (2018)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1735588.mkv&play_token=ifrjAYT39V&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/5Q2pHzDfJ8QlUA2vx2yAXWJkof7.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="Copper Jack Stone purposefully orchestrates a bank robbery in order to be thrown into prison with the notorious Russian kingpin Balam. Balam is more than just a mob criminal; he's a very cunning and dangerous lord who controls the police force from behind bars. Balam lives in prison as a cover for his real power, which is King of the city. His cell is a lavish private room built specifically for him, inaccessible to most in the depths of the prison structure. Even the warden fears venturing into his area of the prison. However, even surrounded by his loyal henchmen and guards in his sectioned off fortress, Balam doesn't know Jack is coming for him to avenge his family, who Balam murdered in cold blood. Balam is tough... but Jack is tougher." year="2015-09-27" director="John Lyde" actors="Matthew Reese, Dolph Lundgren, Danielle C. Ryan, Chuck Liddell, Michael Flynn",Riot (2015)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1727022.mp4&play_token=drFO3kJdHr&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

