#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/o5zHDxx9aGtg0bK9gVghik8ohYb.jpg" group-title="|FR| ACTION/AVENTURE" tvg-type="movie" description="Operating alone in the field for more than 20 years, a CIA hitman uses the 'Help Wanted' section of the newspapers to get his orders from the Agency. His long-lost daughter, now a UK MI6 analyst, tracks him down to deliver shocking news: his CIA boss has been dead for years and the division long since shut down. Together, they set out to discover whose orders he's been executing." year="2024-09-19" director="Roel Reiné" actors="Aaron Eckhart, Tim Roth, Abigail Breslin, Matt Hookings, Lucky Ali",Classified (2024)
