#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/aFjxI9yMd142au1O74JlUttG4Ki.jpg" group-title="|FR| THRILLER/CRIME" tvg-type="movie" description="An assassin on a final assignment in Fuerteventura, to kill a man he has never met. When his target is delayed, he finds himself drawn to the island, people and a ghostly shipwreck. Instead of following protocol he stays. But when the target returns, the world has shifted. Before everything was simple, now nothing is." year="2024-01-26" director="Gonzalo López-Gallego" actors="Ian McShane, Nora Arnezeder, Adam Nagaitis, Thomas Kretschmann, Fanny Ardant",FR - American Star (2024)
