#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/lZGOK0I2DJSRlEPNOAFTSNxSjDD.jpg" group-title="|FR| THRILLER/CRIME" tvg-type="movie" description="When tech billionaire Slater King meets cocktail waitress Frida at his fundraising gala, he invites her to join him and his friends on a dream vacation on his private island. But despite the epic setting, beautiful people, ever-flowing champagne, and late-night dance parties, Frida can sense that there’s something sinister hiding beneath the island’s lush façade." year="2024-08-21" director="Zoë Kravitz" actors="Naomi Ackie, Channing Tatum, Alia Shawkat, Christian Slater, Simon Rex",FR - Blink Twice (2024) LQ
