http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1836318.mkv&play_token=DH4ZpIXMAJ&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/chl53EeJLqg7gkpiuay0Gf0SXL1.jpg" group-title="|FR| COMÉDIE/DRAME" tvg-type="movie" description="Le Docteur Béranger est un célèbre psychanalyste à qui tout réussit. Sa vie serait parfaite s’il n’y avait pas ce patient très angoissé et extrêmement collant : Damien Leroy. Pour enfin s’en débarrasser, il lui fait croire que le seul moyen de guérir est de trouver le grand amour. Mais alors qu’il s’apprête à fêter ses 30 ans de mariage, sa fille Alice lui annonce qu’elle a enfin trouvé l’homme de sa vie qui n’est autre que… Damien. La fête va virer au cauchemar." year="2024-12-11" director="Arnaud Lemort" actors="Christian Clavier, Claire Chust, Baptiste Lecaplain, Cristiana Réali, Rayane Bensetti, Jean-François Cayrey, Laurent Bateau, Claudette Walker, Smadi Wolfman, Élisa Sergent",FR - Jamais sans mon psy (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1830192.mkv&play_token=BB5hvP9z8V&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/3TwP8kSaP9Kar3Jma6w3cfm507x.jpg" group-title="|FR| COMÉDIE/DRAME" tvg-type="movie" description="Anticipating eviction from her retirement home after the death of her son and sole provider, rebellious septuagenarian Émilie decides to take revenge on all those who have wronged her. During her journey of initiation, she cuts to the quick to right the wrongs and is joined by Linda, a cleaning lady with whom she has forged a close bond. She, too, has nothing left to lose and decides to wage war against those who have scorned her. Soon, these two companions are hunted down by a pair of policemen." year="2024-11-22" director="Gustave Kervern" actors="Yolande Moreau, Laure Calamy, Anna Mouglalis, Raphaël Quenard, Marie Gillain",Je ne me laisserai plus faire (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1828318.mkv&play_token=brKT1FCOf0&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

