#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/vcW9sszjdEdvyeLzb6TTVUz080P.jpg" group-title="|FR| COMÉDIE/DRAME" tvg-type="movie" description="Colin, 14, enters a new school and he's freaking out: how do you get by when, like him, you're a stutterer? His meeting with Mr. Devarseau, a charismatic French teacher, will push him to face his fears and break out of his isolation. Now Colin has a group of friends and a project: to go on stage to play Cyrano in front of the whole school." year="2024-11-20" director="Inès de la Bévière, Leïla Gentet, Thomas Metairie, Camille Ganivet, Jennifer Devoldère" actors="José Garcia, Joachim Arseguel, Aure Atika, Claire Dumas, Cédric Vieira",Le Panache (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1816794.mkv&play_token=2L4jzhSowv&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/dRaHoBWFWG23EAEKPQYo1GBcpP9.jpg" group-title="|FR| COMÉDIE/DRAME" tvg-type="movie" description="Pour soutirer de l’argent à ses parents, Benoît demande à une amie de se faire passer pour sa future femme lors d’un séjour en famille au Maroc. Mais lorsque cette dernière se désiste, il n’a pas d’autre choix que de proposer le rôle de sa fausse fiancée… à Fiona, son chauffeur Uber ! La jeune femme, au tempérament impulsif et sans filtre, détonne dans la famille bourgeoise de Benoît." year="2024-09-25" director="Frank Bellocq" actors="Camille Lellouche, Lionel Erdogan, Michèle Laroque, Gérard Darmon, Chloé Astor, Frank Bellocq, Brahim Bihi, Myriam Bourguignon, Clémence Bretécher, Jean-Michel Correia",FR - L'heureuse élue (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1816791.mkv&play_token=bu4c6QAWU5&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/np3mI3KOUcyejEPVzWGSPsAoY2L.jpg" group-title="|FR| COMÉDIE/DRAME" tvg-type="movie" description="Dans le Pigalle des boîtes de nuit, la Beauté professionnelle, c'est Daniela. Quand le client la voit, il a le souffle coupé.Le client vient de gagner gros au Loto. C'est François. Il demande à Daniela « Combien tu prends ' », lui propose immédiatement de devenir sa femme. Elle accepte. Mais on ne quitte pas comme ça Charly, le monde de la nuit..." year="2005-10-26" director="Bertrand Blier" actors="Monica Bellucci, Bernard Campan, Gérard Depardieu, Jean-Pierre Darroussin, François Rollin, Jean Barney, Baptiste Roussillon, Valérie Karsenti, Jean Dell, Sara Forestier",FR Combien tu m'aimes ? (2005)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1816784.mkv&play_token=wtceT58Abs&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/hSts7E4rLqnIjnHBTLECqMBpRPg.jpg" group-title="|FR| COMÉDIE/DRAME" tvg-type="movie" description="Les meilleures amies colocataires Dreux (Keke Palmer) et Alyssa (SZA) sont sur le point de vivre un cauchemar. Lorsqu’elles réalisent que le petit ami d’Alyssa a flambé l’argent du loyer, le duo va prendre tous les moyens, lors d’une hilarante course contre la montre, pour éviter l’expulsion et rester de bonnes amies." year="2025-01-16" director="Lawrence Lamont" actors="Keke Palmer, SZA, Joshua David Neal, Aziza Scott, Patrick Cage, Katt Williams, Maude Apatow, Vanessa Bell Calloway, Gabrielle Dennis, Janelle James",FR - One of Them Days (2025)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1810779.mkv&play_token=tLQ3RxoWJu&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/7GHF2OGsHgqAcDbjGckoeJIbL4f.jpg" group-title="|FR| COMÉDIE/DRAME" tvg-type="movie" description="Dans un monde de plus en plus fou, Lino, qui a décidé de tout plaquer, va se rendre compte que finalement : tout ce qui nous arrive, c’est pour notre bien !" year="2024-09-19" director="Claude Lelouch" actors="Kad Merad, Elsa Zylberstein, Michel Boujenah, Sandrine Bonnaire, Barbara Pravi, Françoise Gillard, Marianne Denicourt, François Morel, Raphaël Mezrahi, Clémentine Célarié",FR - Finalement (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1810777.mkv&play_token=bhAw8x7YlH&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/gC0ZBDJJ2gZEsifLAiWEnY0mn2v.jpg" group-title="|FR| COMÉDIE/DRAME" tvg-type="movie" description="In the Middle Ages a misericorde was a weapon used to put a wounded knight out of his misery. As a theological term, it refers to forgiveness and compassion. In French it has been used as an invocation, notably in Samuel Beckett’s Waiting for Godot: “Christ have mercy on us!” That there may be no one listening (or arriving) remains a central anguish, felt in the depression, addiction and other disorders, that are normal responses to increasingly abnormal culture." year="2024-05-20" director="Nataša Prosenc Stearns" actors="Natasha Maidoff, Carmela Segal, Alan Joseph Marx",FR - Misericorde (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1790134.mkv&play_token=WAIQeitcwK&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/gWRMxWPFkKDv5kh8eKkbYSTsITn.jpg" group-title="|FR| COMÉDIE/DRAME" tvg-type="movie" description="Jo, a young woman and street circus artist, discovers the work of the professional clowns of “Nez pour Rire”. Quickly - perhaps too quickly - entering the association, she found herself at the hospital in contact with children, sick people, caregivers and families, to whom these clowns tirelessly try to bring joy and comfort. ." year="2024-10-14" director="Reda Kateb, Arthur Meynier, Léa mothet, Johana Katz" actors="Aloïse Sauvage, Philippe Rebbot, Sara Giraudeau, Samir Guesmi, Jean-Philippe Buzaud",Sur un fil (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1807591.mkv&play_token=haYgfWW70L&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/4MPZenW0I0AexBbil8das6kupIW.jpg" group-title="|FR| COMÉDIE/DRAME" tvg-type="movie" description="A single mother's struggle to raise a child diagnosed with autism." year="2024-11-13" director="Elsa Truscello, Isabelle Querrioux, Auriane Lacince, John Wax, Leo Bourdon" actors="Audrey Lamy, Nicolas Chupin, Benjamin Tranié, Naidra Ayadi, Jean-Charles Clichet",En tongs au pied de l'Himalaya (2024)
