#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/d8YaaRIDzvHL4NyHJQxIvm0qDng.jpg" group-title="|FR| COMÉDIE/DRAME" tvg-type="movie" description="A famous actress goes incognito to seek treatment for a medical issue, and in a hospital waiting room she meets three remarkable women who help her face adversity with humor and camaraderie." year="2023-02-24" director="Sharon Maymon, Tal Granit" actors="Andie MacDowell, Miriam Margolyes, Sally Phillips, Rakhee Thakrar, Tom Cullen",My Happy Ending (2023)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1788885.mkv&play_token=3SMYytNE9U&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/lEiDGpR7EfLzOfcnoh4nwWcVsqt.jpg" group-title="|FR| COMÉDIE/DRAME" tvg-type="movie" description="Elle est officier de sous-marin tactique. Il est steward. Avant de plonger pour 90 jours elle choisit d’en faire son 'quatre-heures'. Mais le voilà qui s’accroche ! Qui la suit ! Qui la colle ! Où va-t-on si le personnel navigant d’un 747 se targue de romantisme ? Comme si on avait le temps d’être amoureuse à bord d’un bâtiment militaire ! Reste que l’océan Pacifique n’est pas assez grand. L’océan Arctique non plus. Le monde est si petit quand on s’aime d’un si grand amour." year="2024-11-06" director="Lucas Bernard" actors="Pio Marmaï, Eye Haïdara, José Garcia, Victor Pontecorvo, Frédéric Maranber, Paul Zinga, Calixte Broisin-Doutaz, Nicolas Lancelin, Pauline Huruguen, Kevin Bourigault",FR - À toute allure (2024)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1788878.mkv&play_token=3So51JtBsZ&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/7WmpxcBe1kfoWLg0CqTzMILA2LN.jpg" group-title="|FR| COMÉDIE/DRAME" tvg-type="movie" description="La première année de médecine va marquer à jamais le destin de Benjamin et d’Antoine, deux jeunes bacheliers. Une année studieuse faite de renoncement à toute vie sociale, de compétition, de détresse mais aussi d’espoirs." year="2018-09-12" director="Thomas Lilti" actors="Vincent Lacoste, William Lebghil, Michel Lerousseau, Darina Al Joundi, Benoît Di Marco, Graziella Delerm, Guillaume Clérice, Noémi Silvania, Adrien Schmück, Alexandre Blazy",FR - Première année (2018)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1775052.mkv&play_token=eZ9F2LvIMr&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/emWTl62eW3Rwa3KhINahhtILWmr.jpg" group-title="|FR| COMÉDIE/DRAME" tvg-type="movie" description="Léo, a twenty-seven-year-old engineer, has to sell his late father's farmland-his father, a farmer, committed suicide three years earlier-to a rare metals drilling company. However, strange occurrences have led him to believe that the project has been polluting the river since his childhood. He then embarks on a surreal investigation that forces him to confront his grief." year="2024-10-10" director="Lucie Prost, Marylou Weber, Lisa Benard, Manon Coaquette, Lucie Garnavault" actors="Finnegan Oldfield, Florence Loiret Caille, Megan Northam, Andranic Manet, Léna Laurent",Fario (2024)
