#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/wKgRzK743xFWGFarlNt3r6FJCeE.jpg" group-title="|FR| COMÉDIE/DRAME" tvg-type="movie" description="In 1994, Ricardo gave up his dream of being a filmmaker. At twenty-four, he has already, in a way, accepted his destiny: that of a simple citizen, anonymous, lost in the immensity of consumer society. He will never be an artist. A call from Radio-Canada, however, rekindled the artistic flame of the young man whose application was selected among the finalists of the show La Course, 1994-95 Edition." year="2024-07-31" director="Ricardo Trogi" actors="Jean-Carl Boucher, Sandrine Bisson, Claudio Colangelo, Shadi Janho, Youssef Nekmouche",1995 (2024)
